piracy%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20life%20of%20a%20judge%2C%20nothing%20matters%20more%20than%20reputation%20and%20character.%20That%20has%20been%20severely%20tarnished%20and%20irreparably%20damaged.%20The%20baseless%20allegations%20that%20have%20been%20levelled%20against%20me%20have%20proceeded%20on%20mere%20innuendos%20and%20an%20unproven%20assumption%20that%20the%20cash%20allegedly%20seen%20and%20found%20belonged%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Varma%20said%20in%20his%20reply%20to%20a%20three-member%20committee%20formed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Khanna%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20critics%20of%20the%20decision%20to%20transfer%20the%20Delhi%20judge%20is%20former%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%2C%20who%20called%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%20Mr%20Rohatgi%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20said%20the%20matter%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20look%20like%20an%20open%20and%20shut%20case%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20understood%20the%20statement%20that%20this%20transfer%20proposal%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20cash%20scam.%20According%20to%20me%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20cash%20scam%20that%20he%20is%20being%20proposed%20to%20be%20transferred...%20There%20are%20several%20loose%20ends%20in%20this%20case%20as%20of%20now%20which%20need%20to%20be%20answered.%20So%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20any%20great%20thing%20in%20saying%20that%20the%20transfer%20is%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20scam.%20I'm%20actually%20mystified%20by%20this%20statement%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rohatgi%20told%20NDTV%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20press%20note%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20said%20the%20transfer%20was%20not%20linked%20to%20the%20cash%20stash%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743167100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ff4aj2l1_delhi-high-court-judge-justi