20I%20immersed%20myself%20in%20America's%20hustle%20culture%2C%20always%20working%20and%20never%20resting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20first%20worked%20as%20a%20computer%20programmer%20while%20teaching%20part-time%20as%20a%20college%20instructor.%20Later%2C%20I%20transitioned%20into%20marketing%20leadership%2C%20working%20as%20a%20marketing%20manager%20before%20launching%20my%20own%20small%20marketing%20company%20in%20Houston%2C%20TX.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20I%20co-owned%20an%20online%20women's%20beauty%20store%20with%20a%20business%20partner%20and%20pursued%20other%20small%20ventures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20my%20father's%20death%20that%20I%20realized%20my%20sacrifice%3A%20I%20lived%20to%20work%20instead%20of%20working%20to%20live.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20followed%20in%20my%20father's%20footsteps%20as%20a%20workaholic%20and%20realized%20I%20was%20doing%20all%20this%20to%20make%20him%20proud.%20His%20death%20in%202011%20left%20me%20feeling%20aimless.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223608ea2c-3c98-4693-b135-a7f63557d971%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThen%2C%20I%20discovered%20I%20had%20a%20difficult-to-diagnose%20autoimmune%20condition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%202017%2C%20I%20developed%20sudden%20pain%20and%20fatigue%20that%20only%20worsened%20over%20time.%20I%20used%20to%20walk%20three%20to%20four%20miles%20a%20day%20but%20soon%20struggled%20just%20to%20reach%20my%20front%20door.%20Nearly%20every%20joint%20ached%2C%20my%20breathing%20became%20labored%2C%20and%20my%20larger%20muscles%2C%20especially%20my%20thighs%20and%20back%2C%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20constantly%20doing%20resistance%20training.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spent%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eseven%20years%20seeing%20specialists%20and%20undergoing%20countless%20tests%20before%20discovering%20I%20have%20a%20debilitating%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsix-months-to-live-autoimmune-disease-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eautoimmune%20condition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20requires%20medication.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20often%20had%20trouble%20booking%20specialist%20appointments.%20For%20example%2C%20my%20first%20rheumatology%20appointment%20alone%20required%20an%20eight-month%20wait%2C%20all%20while%20I%20suffered%20from%20debilitating%20pain%20and%20fatigue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%20my%20medications%2C%20specialist%20visits%2C%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillions-americans-lose-health-insurance-subsidies-congress-presidential-election-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehealth%20insurance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20costs%2C%20I%20was%20stretching%20my%20budget%20so%20thin%20I%20had%20to%20take%20funds%20from%20retirement%20accounts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20realized%20that%2C%20for%20me%2C%20a%20better%20life%20would%20mean%20somewhere%20I%20could%20afford%20to%20focus%20less%20on%20work%20while%20also%20getting%20the%20healthcare%20I%20needed.%20I%20found%20that%20life%20in%20Mexico%20City.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ad4fad6-56f0-4fdc-a057-85765a457117%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20to%20Mexico%20after%20living%20in%20the%20US%20for%2042%20years%20was%20the%20right%20choice%20for%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20stress%20disappeared.%20Healthcare%20is%20easier%20to%20access%2C%20including%20for%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20getting%20the%20proper%20care%20for%20myself%20felt%20like%20a%20privilege.%20In%20Mexico%2C%20the%20medications%20I%20need%20are%20available%20without%20insurance%20and%20at%20prices%20that%20don't%20require%20financial%20sacrifice.%20For%20example%2C%20one%20of%20my