%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDriving%20systemic%20change%20one%20story%20at%20a%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20struggles%20she%20faced%2C%20Anita%20Mourya%20never%20stopped%20dreaming.%20Even%20as%20she%20stitched%20stones%20onto%20sarees%20late%20into%20the%20night%20by%20candlelight%2C%20she%20imagined%20turning%20her%20craft%20into%20a%20thriving%20business.%20But%20dreaming%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20she%20needed%20support%20to%20take%20that%20leap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20Inclusive%20Entrepreneurship%20programme%2C%20Anita%20had%20access%20to%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20provided%20everything%20she%20needed%20to%20succeed%20(a%20quintessential%20TFMC%20model%20%E2%80%93%20Technology%2C%20Finance%2C%20Market%20and%20Capacity%20Building).%20One%20of%20the%20first%20things%20she%20received%20was%20assistance%20with%20paperwork%20and%20business%20planning.%20Then%20came%20something%20that%20changed%20her%20life%3A%20two%20handheld%20embroidery%20machines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20once%20took%20me%20hours%20to%20complete%20can%20now%20be%20done%20in%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20efficiency%20allowed%20Anita%20to%20scale%20her%20production%20and%20meet%20growing%20demand.%20Soon%2C%20she%20opened%20her%20own%20shop%2C%20specialising%20in%20vibrant%2C%20embellished%20sarees%20and%20bedspreads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20machinery%2C%20the%20programme%20also%20equipped%20Anita%20with%20essential%20business%20skills%20such%20as%20bookkeeping%2C%20stock%20management%2C%20and%20marketing.%20Orders%20began%20pouring%20in%20not%20just%20from%20Mirzapur%20but%20also%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20Ghazipur%2C%20and%20other%20nearby%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the